	   <tr><td colspan=2>I dont know why you would think these are bad earrings.&nbsp;&nbsp;Earrings alone are hard to come by, and usually awarded to tanks for AC, or INT casters.  Most of the clerics I know are still wearing crafted, or forest loops.<br><br>These are awesome because of the hp/mana. Earrings typicly have very low stats on them, so 35/35 is a high rating.  Also click effects are priceless in their own right.  These spells are a pain to pull up, because they are so rarely used.  It so much nicer to pull down a quick key to use the earring, rather than lose a spell slot.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
